Remove product sections with duplicated W-Numbers

Source: R/psmv-xml.R
psmv_xml_remove_duplicated_wNbrs.Rd

Remove product sections with duplicated W-Numbers

Usage

psmv_xml_remove_duplicated_wNbrs(
  psmv_xml = psmv_xml_get(),
  keep = c("last", "first")
)

Arguments

psmv_xml

An object as returned by psmv_xml_get

keep

How should we deal with product sections with identical W-Numbers? The default strategy 'keep' only keeps the last of such sets of product sections.

Value

An 'psmv_xml' object with only product sections that have unique W-Numbers

Examples

psmv_xml_remove_duplicated_wNbrs()
